data.description: Like new home in a quiet neighborhood sitting on 3 acres! As you come in from the front porch you enter a gorgeous vaulted great room with an abundance of natural light. The kitchen has granite countertops and floating shelves with a walk-in pantry. Primary bedroom, bathroom and closet wrap around to a large laundry room that leads into mudroom/drop zone. Two separate bedrooms and full bath on the opposite side of the home make up for a great split floorpan. The back patio is covered with a TV and an extension of a wood deck that partially wraps the above ground pool. Agents see remarks.
